parameters: Memimi: Ooooooooh...! I won't lose, you...!!

Shark Broccoli-Mayor: Gaaah... No way... Where does she get
such strength...? Being pushed back... Losing...? Me, of all
people...?

Shark Broccoli-Mayor: No, this cannot be allowed...!! Come
forth, my underlings!!! Defeat this girl and I'll give you a
million yen---!!!

Memimi: Wha... How cowardly...! Ugh... I don't have the
strength to fight a new opponent... Not anymore...
Memimi: Ah... Everyone...! You came for me...?

Bunny-chan: We couldn't stand by and do nothing, so we all
came together♪ Memimi-chan, I brought a spare Shark Suit!
And we bought back the Monster Parts that were listed on
MolCar!

Brachiocondor: To think we've cornered that Shark Mayor this
far!! Just a little more, put on my Monster Parts and finish
it!!

Anomalocaris Mosman: Mosmos... I'm glad I followed you~!!
Use my Monster Parts too... It's going to be a battle for
the history books in Monster Fight!!

Cerberus Octopus: My Monster Parts are expensive, you
know... Giving them to you twice is a huge service, just for
this time! Win against that guy and pay me back tenfold!!

Drillmaid: I bowed my head to Shark Broccoli's older
brothers to have them come here... It's not my place to say,
but I want you to inherit everyone's feelings once more... I
want to atone for the chaos I've caused in the city...

: Go forth, Duke Shark...!! Save Orca Asparagus... And now,
entrust our long-cherished dream of uniting all
organizations with the Monster Parts!!

Memimi: Thank you so much, Great Leader-sama...
Everyone...!! I can feel the power surging within me!!

Shark Broccoli-Mayor: Im... Impossible...!! She's regaining
her strength... Such nonsense, this can't be happening!!!

With the power of her friends, Memimi regained her monster
form and the counterattack began...!
